data.description: This unique place has a style all its own. Stylish innovation within one of LA’s most historical neighborhoods at The Montebello South! Enjoy a beautiful new community of smart townhomes complete with all­ inclusive Live Green amenities and modern exteriors. Close to shopping, dining, entertainment, and outdoor recreation all within a charming neighborhood. It will be easy to discover what makes this home so special.    This home is located 15 minutes away from downtown LA. This property features two bedrooms and three bathrooms. New vinyl flooring and Solar powered panels.    First floor: is a two car garage with direct access into the inside and a closet on the same floor.  Second floor: Open floor design next to a bathroom, with a large island in the kitchen opening to the dining area and living room, as well as large sliding doors leading to a balcony with outside furniture.  Third floor: A spacious master suite with double sinks. Tempered glass shower with separate walk-in closet, the second bedroom also has a large walk-in closet and its own full bathroom. A laundry facility is in between both bedrooms.
